      "wikitext": "{{Infobox villager\n|portrait  = Governor.png\n|birthday  = Unknown\n|address   = Unknown\n|marriage  = No\n|favorites = N/A\n|toc = n\n}}\n{{Quote|What a lovely occasion... It's always a joy to visit Stardew Valley.|Governor}}\n\nThe '''Governor''' is the governor of the region that [[Pelican Town]] is a part of. He attends the [[Luau]] annually and tastes the local food. The Governor is also referenced in the [[Lobster Bisque]] episode of [[The Queen of Sauce]] and can appear in the [[Movie Theater]] lobby.\n\n==Quotes==\n'''[[Luau|The Luau]]'''\n<br />''Odd Years''\n{{Squote|What a lovely occasion... It's always a joy to visit Stardew Valley.<br />I must speak to the missus about purchasing a vacation home here.}}\n''Even Years''\n{{Squote|I eagerly anticipate my visit to Stardew Valley each year. There's a palpable charm in the air!}}\n'''in the [[Movie Theater]]'''\n{{Squote|It's lovely to see economic development in the valley!}}\n{{Squote|I really must bring the missus out for soup and a movie!}}\n\n==Portraits==\n<gallery mode=\"packed\" class=\"portraitgallery\">\nFile:Governor.png\nFile:Governor Neutral.png\nFile:Governor Examine.png\nFile:Governor Sick.png\n</gallery>\n\n{{NavboxVillagers}}\n\n[[Category:NPCs]]\n\n[[de:Gouverneur]]\n[[es:Gobernador]]\n[[fr:Gouverneur]]\n[[it:Governatore]]\n[[ja:市長]]\n[[ko:도지사]]\n[[hu:Kormányzó]]\n[[pt:Governador]]\n[[ru:Губернатор]]\n[[tr:Vali]]\n[[zh:州长]]"
